Package: qshap
Type: Package
Title: Fast Calculation of Feature Contributions in Boosting Trees
Version: 1.0
Date: 2026-03-02
Authors@R: c(person("Steven", "He", role = "aut", email = "hess1@uci.edu"), person("Zhongli", "Jiang", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "zhongli.jiang.stats@gmail.com"), person("Dabao", "Zhang", role = "aut", email = "zdb969@hs.uci.edu"))
Description: Computes feature-specific R-squared values using 'Shapley' decomposition
 of the total R-squared for boosting tree models in polynomial time.
 The package supports models fitted with 'XGBoost' and 'LightGBM', and
 provides efficient parallel implementations for large-scale problems.
 The methodology is described in Jiang, Zhang and Zhang (2025)
 <https://dl.acm.org/doi/10.5555/3762387.3762469>.
